Bankai_Tensa_Zangetsu.name = Bankai – Tensa Zangetsu
Bankai_Tensa_Zangetsu.description = Bankai – Tensa Zangetsu is a legendary spiritual blade. Its black edge with a chain focuses the wielder’s energy, releasing the devastating wave <i><b>Getsuga Tensho — «Moon Fang That Pierces the Heavens»</b></i>. 
Shikai_Tensa_Zangetsu.name = Shikai – Zangetsu
Shikai_Tensa_Zangetsu.description = Zangetsu is a massive spiritual cleaver, permanently in its released state. The black blade, wrapped in living cloth, empowers its wielder, unleashing <i><b>Getsuga Tensho</b></i> waves and serving as a shield against physical and energy-based attacks.
ReiryokuCrystal.name = Reiryoku Crystal
ReiryokuCrystal.description = A crystal of pure spiritual energy, a concentration of numerous souls. Awakens and evolves a Zanpakuto.
Sealed_Zangetsu.name = Sealed – Zangetsu
Sealed_Zangetsu.description = The sealed blade before awakening. Holds boundless, yet dormant potential.
Asauchi.name = Asauchi
Asauchi.description = A blank soul template. The foundation for a future Zanpakuto, awaiting the imprint of its owner.
Sode_No_Shirayuki.name = Shikai – Sode no Shirayuki
Sode_No_Shirayuki.description = An elegant ice katana. Its release command, \n<i><b>«Dance, Sode no Shirayuki»</b></i> commands cold and beauty.
Shikai_Wabisuke.name = Shikai – Wabisuke
Shikai_Wabisuke.description = An elegantly curved sword whose treacherous nature is the opposite of its external refinement. Its strike places a curse of weight upon the target. With each parry or block, the victim's burden relentlessly doubles, until the opponent is broken and pinned to the ground by their own unbearable load. Release command: <i><b>«Bend, Wabisuke»</b></i>.
Shikai_Hozukimaru.name = Shikai – Hozukimaru
Shikai_Hozukimaru.description = A crude and straightforward war spear. Its simple, unadorned form conceals a fierce destructive power and unyielding durability. Within this weapon lies a dormant potential for transformation, capable of unlocking its true, even more formidable form.
Shikai_Kyoka_Suigetsu.name = Shikai – Kyoka Suigetsu
Shikai_Kyoka_Suigetsu.description = An unassuming katana, eternally in its released state. Its true power is not steel, but absolute sensory dominion. Those who witness its release ritual become forever trapped in its perfect hypnosis, seeing a world sculpted by the wielder's will. A weapon that conquers reality through perception.
Sealed_Kenpachi_Zanpakuto.name = Sealed – Kenpachi's Zanpakuto
Sealed_Kenpachi_Zanpakuto.description = A massive, crude and rusted cleaver. This is the sealed state of a Zanpakuto belonging to a warrior of monstrous spiritual pressure. Its jagged, unrefined form and tattered wrappings are self-imposed limitations, allowing the wielder to savor the thrill of battle longer. The true power within is dormant, awaiting acknowledgment.
Shikai_Benihime.name = Shikai – Benihime
Shikai_Benihime.description = An elegant, slightly curved saber with a crimson motif. Upon its command, <i><b>«Awaken, Benihime»</b></i>, it gains the power to launch precise <i>Crimson Shots</i>, erect near-impenetrable hexagonal shields, and weave razor-sharp nets of spiritual energy. A versatile blade perfect for both calculated offense and absolute defense.
True_Bankai_Tensa_Zangetsu.name = True Bankai – Tensa Zangetsu
True_Bankai_Tensa_Zangetsu.description = The ultimate evolution of Ichigo's power. This form consolidates his dual blades into a single, immense black cleaver wrapped in stark white bandages. It represents the full convergence of his spiritual heritage, focusing overwhelming force into a singular, devastating edge.
True_Shikai_Zangetsu.name = True Shikai – Zangetsu
True_Shikai_Zangetsu.description = Ichigo's true Shikai, manifested as two distinct black blades. The massive cleaver embodies his fused Shinigami and Hollow powers, while the smaller knife represents his Quincy heritage. Release command: <i><b>«Unite and Protect, Zangetsu»</b></i>. The blades can fire\n<i>Getsuga Tensho</i> independently or combine them into a devastating cross-shaped wave, <i><b>Getsuga Jujisho</b></i>.


Soul_Imprinting_Altar.name = Soul Imprinting Altar
Soul_Imprinting_Altar.description = A sacred workstation where the wielder's soul merges with the Asauchi. Through deep meditation and concentration of spiritual energy (Reiryoku), the foundation of the future Zanpakuto is laid. This altar is used not only for the initial awakening but also for the subsequent stages of the blade's evolution — from Shikai to the ultimate revelation, Bankai.

Shinigami_Robes.name = Shinigami Robe – Shihakusho
Shinigami_Robes.description = The standard Shinigami uniform worn by all members of the Gotei 13.
Shinigami_Robes_Sleeveless.name = Shinigami Robe – Sleeveless
Shinigami_Robes_Sleeveless.description = A modified <i>Shihakusho</i> for those who desire more liberty of movement. More considered a cosmetic modification to the standard uniform.
Shinigami_Robes_Captain.name = Shinigami Robe – Captain
Shinigami_Robes_Captain.description = The white coat worn by Captains over their standard uniform. Provides superior spiritual protection and denotes highest rank in the Gotei 13.


Resonating_Reishi_Core.name = Resonating Reishi Core
Resonating_Reishi_Core.description = This core hums at a frequency that mimics yours. It's an extension of your soul. Ready to be assigned to a blade to awaken it.
Transcendent_Essence.name = Transcendent Essence
Transcendent_Essence.description = A swirling paradox of absolute power. The boundaries between your spirit and the physical world have dissolved into this singular pulsing point. Within this glow lies the true form of your soul, screaming to be released.



items.Currency_Kan.name = Kan
items.Currency_Kan.description = The standard currency of the Soul Society. A single Kan represents the value of one bale of rice in the world of the living. Its weight and ring are said to be tuned to the very frequency of reishi, making it impossible to counterfeit. To a merchant in the Rukongai, this coin is a fortune; to a captain, mere pocket change.

items.Medical_Pill_Basic.name = Basic Medical Pill
items.Medical_Pill_Basic.description = A standard-issue pill from Squad 4's medical corps. Made from concentrated medicinal herbs and a trace of healing kaido energy.\n\nRestores <color is="#ffffff">30%</color> health instantly.

items.Kaido_Infused_Pill.name = Kaido-Infused Restoration Pill
items.Kaido_Infused_Pill.description = A masterpiece of Squad 4's medical research. Not merely a pill, but a solid capsule of suspended healing kaido spells.\n\nRestores <color is="#ffffff">100%</color> health instantly and grants:\n\n• <color is="#ffffff">Health Regen II</color>\n\nDuration: <color is="#ffffff">0:30</color>